    public class LSDTransformer
extends com.mumfrey.liteloader.transformers.event.EventInjectionTransformer
    Internal class. This transformer injects a 20 tps callback at the same location as FML's post-client tick event, so that LSDGameTickEvent will behave consistently across the two loaders.
